  <div class="review__wrapper">
    <div class="review__content--item boxed row">
      <div class="review__content--label col-sm-10">
        <h2 class="margin-above--none">
          <span class="fal fa-box-usd fa-icons"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="font-weight-heavy">Annuities &amp; pensions </span></h2>
        <div class="key-value-group margin-above">
          <div class="key">
            <h4>Account ownership</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="value">My account
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="key-value-group margin-above">
          <div class="key">
            <h4>Product reference number</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="value">098 765 432
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-2" style="margin: 0;"><button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onClick="editCard('annuities-and-pensions');">&nbsp;Edit&nbsp;</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- Open card -->
<div id="annuities-and-pensions-card" class="boxed margin-above margin-below" style="display: none;">
  <div>
    <h2 class="margin-above--none" style="display: inline-block;">
      <span class="fal fa-box-usd fa-icons"></span>&nbsp;<span class="font-weight-heavy">Annuities &amp; pensions</span></h2><button id="deleteButton" class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary small warning floated"
      onclick="removeSummary('annuities-and-pensions');">&nbsp;Delete item&nbsp;
    </button>
  </div>
  <div id="card-details" class="margin-below--large">
    <p class="margin-below--mid margin-above">Add all your income, and your partner’s income, so we can calculate your payments.</p>
    <p>A series of regular payments made for a lifetime or a fixed period by a financial institution, superannuation fund or retirement savings account. </p>
    <p>Includes payments from account-based pensions, allocated pensions, transition to retirement pensions, market linked pensions, term allocated pensions, immediate annuities and
      account-based annuities.</p>
    <p>Do not include defined benefit superannuation pensions.</p>
    <form id="myForm">
      <input type="reset" style="display:none">
      <!-- form goes here -->
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="income-stream">Do you (or your partner) receive income from an income stream? </label>
        <div class="radio-toggle">
          <label class="on label-left" for="yes-income-stream">
            <input id="yes-income-stream" type="radio" name="income-stream">
            <span>Yes</span>
          </label>
          <label class="off label-right" for="no-income-stream">
            <input id="no-income-stream" type="radio" name="income-stream">
            <span>No</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group margin-above--large">
        <label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="drop-down">Who owns the account?</label>
        <select class="uikit-text-input input-half" id="drop-down" name="drop-down">
          <option selected="selected">-- Select one --</option>
          <option>Me</option>
          <option>My partner</option>
          <option>Both me and my partner</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="Input field">Who is the provider</label>
        <input class="uikit-text-input input-half" name="Input field" id="Input field" type="text" value="" required aria-required="true">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="Input field">Product reference number</label>
        <input class="uikit-text-input input-half" name="Input field" id="Input field" type="text" value="" required aria-required="true">
      </div>

      <div class="uikit-page-alerts" role="alert">
        <p>You will need to attach a certified copy of documents which provide the latest details of each income stream. Your provider should be able to provide you with an ‘income
          stream schedule’ for each income stream product. </p>
      </div>

    </form>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div id="buttonset2" class="form-group margin-above--none">
    <button id="addButton" class="uikit-btn" onclick="addSummary('annuities-and-pensions');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Add&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</button> &nbsp;<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary"
      onclick="cancelCard();">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Cancel&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</button>
  </div>
</div>